comments: Brissett (BOS) is imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Sabonis (SAC) legally contests Mykhailiuk's (BOS) jump shot attempt.
Brissett (BOS) reaches for the rebound and marginal contact occurs with Murray's (SAC) arm as he fails to secure the loose ball.
Murray (SAC) legally contests Hauser's (BOS) driving shot attempt.
Mykhailiuk (BOS) retreats alongside Fox's (SAC) path and absorbs the marginal body contact as they come together at the end of the drive.
Mykhailiuk (BOS) legally contests Fox's (SAC) jump shot attempt.
Brissett (BOS) initiates contact with Sabonis' (SAC) arm, which affects Sabonis' ability to maintain control of the ball.
Jones (SAC) maintains a legal guarding position as he defends Pritchard (BOS) at the end of the drive.
Sabonis (SAC) legally contests and cleanly blocks Pritchard's (BOS) jump shot attempt.
Pritchard (BOS) makes clean contact with the ball and avoids any contact with Fox's (SAC) arm as he contests the jump shot attempt.
Murray (SAC) makes clean contact with the ball to dislodge it from Hauser (BOS) during the driving shot attempt.
Hauser (BOS) makes clean contact with the ball and deflects away Murray's (SAC) pass attempt.
Barnes (SAC) legally contests Tillman's (BOS) shot attempt.
Pritchard (BOS) is retreating alongside Fox's (SAC) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together at the end of the drive.
Hauser (BOS) legally contests Fox's (SAC) jump shot attempt.
Brissett (BOS) reaches for the rebound and marginal contact occurs with Barnes' (SAC) wrist as he is unable to secure the loose ball.
Brissett (BOS) briefly rests his forearm on Murray's (SAC) body and marginal contact occurs during Murray's shot attempt in the lane.
Mykhailiuk (BOS) follows through and initiates illegal contact with Jones' (SAC) face after he tips the ball.
